  "texts": [
    "We conducted a placebo test to exclude the influence caused by other random factors.",
    "The single-period DID model usually adopts the method of changing the policy time or",
    "the experimental group to perform placebo tests; however, the policy time point of our experimental group is not the same.",
    "To resolve this issue, we randomly select the experimental group and change the time point of green bond issuance to construct a pseudoexperimental group and a pseudopolicy time point, following Chen and Xie (2022).",
    "We randomly repeated the processes 1000 times to conduct the mixed placebo test."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}